      <title>AI 初创公司估值达 5 亿美元，与竞争对手联络中心竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/ai-startup-hits-500-million-valuation-to-rival-contact-centers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一群经验丰富的硅谷高管为一家提供人工智能增强型联络中心服务的新创公司筹集了 5000 万美元，加入了众多希望颠覆传统外包的公司行列。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/ai-startup-hits-500-million-valuation-to-rival-contact-centers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
